criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        1. patients over 18 years of age undergone MCCG examination in Changhai Hospital

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. pregnancy or suspected pregnancy;

          2. suspected or known intestinal stenosis;

          3. pacemaker, other implanted electro medical devices which could interfere with magnetic
             resonance; (4) undergone a known surgery which could possibly affect visualization of
             the duodenal papilla;

        (5) other conditions which may lead to capsule retention.
